---
title: Spiced Pork Patties with Tomato Pan Sauce plus Rainbow Vegetable Jumble
description: If you love meatballs and you love burgers, you’re going to go batty for these patties! First you’ll form pork meatballs with minced onion and our Tunisian-inspired blend of smoky-savory spices. Then, you’ll smash the meatballs into juicy patties right in the pan to create extra-crispy edges. Meanwhile a colorful combo of carrot, zucchini, and red onion are roasting in the oven. That’s yummy enough, it’s true, but we wouldn’t leave you high and dry—you’ll make a quick tomato-y pan sauce to top it all off!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-pork-patties-with-tomato-pan-sauce-ec621f9d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spiced-pork-patties-with-tomato-pan-sauce-6434ec400f57500e1b084f12-2ac29568.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spiced-pork-patties-with-tomato-pan-sauce-6434ec400f57500e1b084f12
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: Mediterranean
nutrition:
  calories: 500 kcal
  fat: 35 g
  saturated fat: 12 g
  carbohydrates: 21 g
